*** This file describes the installation of the sgml-powertools package ***

You need to do the following things to get sgml-powertools installed:

o Check Makefile for local modifications (and Makefiles in tools/* directories)

o Make tools and translation specific programs with "make".

o Install tools with "make install"

(Note, you must be root to install in /usr/local and other system directories)

o the contrib directory has some interesting programs that may be
  useful to you

o Documentation from the LinuxDoc and Qwertz distributions are retained for 
  the time being. 

